## How to run

```bash
npm install
# .env is already generated; fill in missing API keys
npm start
```

## Environment variables required

{{#if (eq wallet "cdp-server-wallet")}}
- `CDP_API_KEY_ID` — Coinbase Developer Platform key ID
- `CDP_API_KEY_SECRET` — CDP secret
- `CDP_WALLET_SECRET` — Wallet encryption secret
{{/if}}
{{#if isBankr}}
- `BANKR_API_KEY` — API key for Bankr client
{{/if}}
{{#if isSponge}}
- `SPONGE_API_KEY` — API key for Sponge wallet access
{{/if}}
{{#if hasVirtuals}}
- `VIRTUALS_ACP_BIN` — ACP CLI executable name/path (defaults to `acp`)
{{/if}}
{{#if isVenice}}
- `VENICE_API_KEY` — Venice API key
- `VENICE_BASE_URL` — optional override (defaults to `https://api.venice.ai/api/v1`)
{{else}}
- `LLM_API_KEY` — API key for {{llm}}
{{/if}}
